lookupPrinters(BBjInt f_client%) - method in class PrintUtils

lookupPrinters: alternate version of BBjAPI().lookupPrinters purpose: workaround for this problem: These sources describe the problem from Java's point of view https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-8182683 https://bugs.openjdk.java.net/browse/JDK-8180347 basically the JVM sporadically crashes on some Windows systems when looking up printers so this method tries to use powershell to lookup the printers instead of the Java internal method falling back to the BBj version
